            section#about.section
                #about-text.section-content
                    h1.show-on-scroll Strathclyde's Space Society since 2011.
                    p.show-on-scroll StrathSEDS runs talks, events and workshops aimed at giving students a link to the space industry. During the semester we hold meetings on Tuesdays and Thursdays at 5pm. On Tuesdays we hold one-off sessions designed to give students an environment to grow their interest in space and gain skills necassary to work in the industry. Thursdays are dedicated to working on projects such as Strathosphere I. 
        
